    <IsekaiLeveling.SkillTree.PassiveTreeDef>
        <defName>PassiveTree_Mage</defName>
        <label>Mage</label>
        <treeClass>Mage</treeClass>
        <treeDescription>Wielders of arcane power, mages channel intelligence and wisdom into unstoppable mental force. Five constellations diverge from the mage's core — each refining a distinct facet of their boundless intellect and psychic potential. Keep psyfocus high to unleash Arcane Overflow.</treeDescription>
        <classGimmick>ArcaneOverflow</classGimmick>
        <classGimmickName>Arcane Overflow</classGimmickName>
        <classGimmickDescription>The higher a mage's psyfocus, the more arcane energy overflows from their mind — amplifying psychic sensitivity and mental acuity. Arcane Overflow scales along the Archmage's Path. Tier 1 (Acolyte): above 50% psyfocus → up to +20% Psychic Sensitivity. Tier 2 (Adept): above 40% → up to +35%. Tier 3 (Magister): above 30% → up to +55%. Tier 4 (Archmage): above 20% → up to +80%. Also boosts research speed at half strength. Scales linearly — maximum bonus at 100% focus.</classGimmickDescription>

